{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, smaller open-access models, when RAG-enhanced, exhibited comparable levels of accuracy and specificity to larger models.",
    "Our findings indicate that RAG-enhanced LLMs have the potential to improve ICD-10-CM coding accuracy in emergency departments, thereby lowering administrative load and increasing coding efficiency.",
    "The equivalent performance of smaller, RAG-enhanced models to bigger ones demonstrates the scalability and efficiency of this method.",
    "Future studies should focus on the practical use of these technologies, such as their integration into existing hospital systems and their influence on clinical workflows and patient outcomes.",
    "Characteristics of the large language models (LLMs) used in the study."
  ]
}